### 5. CATS Data Model
* **Presenter**: Juan Deng
* **Slides**: [3.2-draft-yl-cats-data-model-07](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-cats-slides-for-draft-yl-cats-data-model-07-00)
* **Discussion**:
  * Juan Deng presented the YANG data model for CATS, detailing the CATS Computing Information Base (CIB), the CATS Network Information Base (NIB), the southbound interface (SBI), and the CSMA API.
