### 6. Distribution of Service Metadata in BGP-LS
* **Presenter**: Mo Young Han
* **Slides**: [3.3-Distribution of Service Metadata in BGP-LS](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-cats-33distribution-of-service-metadata-in-bgp-ls-00)
