## Decisions and Action Items

1. **YANG Doctor Review**: The chairs agreed to request a YANG Doctors review for `draft-yl-cats-data-model-07` to validate its structure and syntax.
2. **Incorporate Operational Metrics/Semantics**: Authors of `draft-ietf-cats-metric-definition` will work with the authors of `draft-zhangb-cats-service-metrics-op` and `draft-zhu-cats-metric-semantics` to fold relevant operational/freshness concepts into the main metrics draft prior to starting Working Group Last Call.
3. **Protocol Requirements Priority**: The working group reaffirmed its commitment to focus on defining and agreeing upon protocol *requirements* within the CATS WG before pursuing solution drafts in downstream protocol working groups (e.g., IDR, PCE, LSR).

